      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. Equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing, the engine pulls strongly to redline with that signature boxer howl. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension that provides exceptional mechanical grip and communicative steering feedback. While showing signs of careful use, this example is mechanically robust, offering a pure, analog driving experience with sharp throttle response and confident braking performance.",
